Package: RmvLMM
Title: A Rotated Multivariate Linear Mixed Model for Dual Large-Scale GWAS
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qinyuan", "Zhang", 
           email = "zhangqinyuan19@mails.ucas.ac.cn", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Qizhai", "Li", 
           role = "aut")
  )
Description: RmvLMM is a powerful and scalable statistical framework for multi-trait GWAS 
    on biobank-scale samples. It employs orthogonal rotation to decorrelate traits and 
    a fast iterative algorithm for covariance estimation.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
